{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Create a tax break for workers who were not furloughed during the pandemic",
        "additional_details": "Thousands of works continued to work while thousands more were being paid by the Government not to work.\r\n \r\nWe believe it is not fair that workers who were not furloughed during the pandemic have to pay the same tax as those who were. Workers who were not furloughed should receive a tax break, to reflect the fact they did not benefit from this scheme.\r\n",
        "background": "The Government should create a tax break for workers who were not furloughed during the covid-19 pandemic.",
